title: 'Disable the exim_can_connect_db SELinux Boolean'

description: |-
    By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>exim_can_connect_db</tt> is disabled.
    If this setting is enabled, it should be disabled.
    <sebool-macro enable="false" sebool="exim_can_connect_db" />

